{"tid":726361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國又輸] 美國6月大豆庫存創新高 憂關稅報復後滯銷","createTime":"2018-07-02T10:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T08:40:08.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d84b9cc9ab06cac5621b66d28b874f18b9cd87ce","tid":726361,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T10:23:55.000Z","msg":"美國6月大豆庫存創新高 憂關稅報復後滯銷<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180702002030-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180702002030-260408&d=wJQDztqai%2BickeFlznggjb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=80ba6d9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180702002030-260408</a><br />\n<br />\n美國農業部（USDA）6月29日發布的數據顯示，截至6月1日，美國的大豆庫存比去年同期增加26%，達到約12億蒲式耳（約422.86億公升），創出6月的單月最高庫存紀錄。此前，受到對大陸出口增加影響，美國豆農持續增產大豆。<br />\n<br />\n但如果7月6日美國對大陸商品啟動徵收追加關稅，受大陸方面的報復性關稅措施影響，約占美國大豆產量3分之1的對大陸大豆出口將受到打擊。2019年以後美國的大豆庫存可能進一步增加，並壓低價格。<br />\n<br />\n美國農業部的數據顯示，美國2018年的大豆種植面積約為8960萬英畝，達到過去第2大的水準。大豆種植面積僅比最大時的2017年小1%。此外，大豆種植面積自1983年以來時隔35年超過了玉米的種植面積，也反映了美國農戶種植大豆的強烈意願。<br />\n<br />\n(旺報 )"},{"pid":"5ff2013a937261dea5b6d15af08f356f88422851","tid":726361,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T10:25:29.000Z","msg":"支那times<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365b94ade6639243d3974ea96c3ba71d4f8a5233","tid":726361,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T10:26:19.000Z","msg":"好心就改名叫taiwantimes啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d9e074501d881e1b3b28346eb331460af2dd0b7","tid":726361,"uid":45657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"365b94ade6639243d3974ea96c3ba71d4f8a5233","tid":726361,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T10:26:19.000Z","msg":"好心就改名叫taiwantimes啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T10:35:49.000Z","msg":"人哋心繫支那又話你知咩"},{"pid":"c37b2c2a6ffe9ca50a9b5a964bb7f506c6c90a56","tid":726361,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T10:45:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過多未用嚟做生物燃料<br />\n之前試過<br />\n但就推高大豆價格而停左"},{"pid":"be4b179b50a37216501b4acfc6eaeb0b84a21b54","tid":726361,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T00:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ef4881cf7b48c06861861e9b33cb42cf7ab812","tid":726361,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c37b2c2a6ffe9ca50a9b5a964bb7f506c6c90a56","tid":726361,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T10:45:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過多未用嚟做生物燃料<br />\n之前試過<br />\n但就推高大豆價格而停左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:40:08.000Z","msg":"obama 先會咁玩，trump trump 要玩煤"}]}